content: Howdy, my name is Connor Kammlah and I am a sophomore engineering major from Austin, Texas; but more importantly I am THE loudest and THE proudest member of the Fightin’ Texas Aggie class of 2023 (A-A-A-A-A)! Not only am I a Redass Aggie, but I love to cook, watch the ICONIC Aggie band, and go on road trips! I am also a proud co-chair of the Service League committee with Maisey Martinez! I can’t wait to meet you class of ‘24!!
name: Connor Kammlah
